every Muslim.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he has nothing?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen he should work with his hands to benefit himself and give in charity.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat if he cannot do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9806,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/14\/every-joint-charity-due\/","url_meta":{"origin":885,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Every joint has charity due, even a good word","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCharity is due upon every joint of the people for every day upon which the sun rises. Justly reconciling two people is charity. Helping a man with his animal and lifting his luggage upon it is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/kull-maruf-sadaqah-smiling\/","url_meta":{"origin":885,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Every good deed is charity, even smiling","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery good deed is charity. Verily, it is a good deed to meet your brother with a smiling face, and to pour what is left from your bucket into your brother's vessel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32285,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/360-acts-of-charity-due\/","url_meta":{"origin":885,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Every day 360 acts of charity are due","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every human being among the children of Adam was created with three hundred and sixty joints. Whoever exalts Allah, praises Allah, declares Allah is one, glorifies Allah, removes a rock from the roads of people, or a thorn,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/every-morning-joints-owe\/","url_meta":{"origin":885,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Every morning your joints owe charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cUpon every one of your joints in the morning is charity due. Every glorification of Allah is charity. Every praise of Allah is charity. Every declaration of the oneness of Allah is charity. Every exaltation of Allah is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/22\/all-good-deeds-are-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":885,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: All good deeds rewarded, even smiling","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not belittle any good deed, even meeting your brother with a cheerful face.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0630\u064e\u0631\u064d\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u0627\u064e \u062a\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0642\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/885","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"e